    if (pw.length() < 8) throw new IllegalArgumentException();
}
```
Secure:
```
void validate(String pw) {
    if (pw.length() < 8) throw new IllegalArgumentException();
    if (contextWords.matches(pw))
        throw new IllegalArgumentException("banned context word");
}
```

